<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='ruby'><span class='line'> <span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">checkout</span> <span class="n">master</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">&lt;p&gt;$ git merge –no-ff fixbug-1.1.1&lt;/</span><span class="nb">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nb">p</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">$</span> <span class="n">git</span> <span class="n">tag</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">a</span> <span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="sr">/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="sr">&lt;p&gt;$ git push origin 1.1.1`</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>bug 修复完成，合并回 <code>master</code> 并打上版本号；</p>

